                            <comment id="17469978" author="jmckenzie" created="Thu, 6 Jan 2022 15:44:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1. Had a question about whether inheriting the 10 second timeout w/out revising it makes sense from a &quot;brittleness and future containerized test execution environments will make us sad&quot; perspective but still; this should fix it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
